SEEDS : the people who are using the torrent client and finished downloading the movie , game.....etc and they are in seeding mode (that means we take the movie , game etc........and if the seeders is zero then....you cannot download the movie , game cause there isnt anyone grab the file from & if the seeders increased that means the download speed increase
LEECHERS : the people that are downloading the file (movie , game)
and havent finished yet.....and if the leechers increased that means the network will ne crowded and the download speed will be reduced 
so better seeders better torrent

so that means download speed = seeds / leechers
